name: instAB5ModuleCat
initialProofState:
R : Type u
inst✝ : Ring R
⊢ CategoryTheory.AB5 (ModuleCat R)
decl:
instance : AB5 (ModuleCat.{u} R) where
  ofShape J _ _ :=
    HasExactColimitsOfShape.domain_of_functor J (forget₂ (ModuleCat R) AddCommGrp)
